Configuration is possible either via environment variables or java properties.

Possible configuration options:
	BROKER_URL - The url of the ActiveMQ broker. Default is 'tcp://localhost:61616'
	MONGO_URL - The url of the MongoDB. Default is 'localhost'
	EXTRACTION_QUEUE_NAME - The name of the ActiveMQ queue for extraction. Default is 'tweet-extraction'
	FOLLOWS_QUEUE_NAME - The name of the ActiveMQ queue for follows. Default is 'tweet-follows'
	MONGO_DATABASE - The name of the MongoDB database. Default is 'twitterdb'
	MONGO_COLLECTION - The name of the MongoDB database collection. Default is 'statuses'